extends _layouts/default

- var title = "Case Study: FinTech Startup - 300% Revenue Growth | TechCorp"
- var description = "How TechCorp helped a fintech startup scale from 10K to 1M users with cloud infrastructure and AI-powered fraud detection."
- var activeNav = "services"
- var ogType = "article"

block append headStyles
  style.
    .case-study-layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
      gap: var(--ms-space-12);
      align-items: start;
    }
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .case-study-layout {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
    .case-study-sidebar {
      position: sticky;
      top: calc(100px + var(--ms-space-6));
    }
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .case-study-sidebar {
        position: static;
      }
    }
    .sidebar-card {
      background-color: var(--ms-bg-secondary);
      border-radius: var(--ms-radius-lg);
      padding: var(--ms-space-8);
    }
    .sidebar-item {
      padding: var(--ms-space-3) 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ms-border-light);
    }
    .sidebar-item:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .sidebar-label {
      font-size: var(--ms-text-xs);
      font-weight: var(--ms-font-semibold);
      color: var(--ms-text-tertiary);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: var(--ms-tracking-wider);
      margin-bottom: var(--ms-space-1);
    }
    .sidebar-value {
      font-size: var(--ms-text-sm);
      color: var(--ms-text-primary);
    }
    .metrics-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: var(--ms-space-6);
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .metrics-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
    .metric-card {
      text-align: center;
      padding: var(--ms-space-8);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--ms-brand-primary) 0%, var(--ms-brand-accent) 100%);
      border-radius: var(--ms-radius-lg);
      color: #fff;
    }
    .metric-value {
      font-size: var(--ms-text-4xl);
      font-weight: var(--ms-font-bold);
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: var(--ms-space-2);
    }
    .metric-label {
      font-size: var(--ms-text-sm);
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

block content
  //- Hero
  section.ms-hero.ms-hero--subpage
    .ms-hero__container
      p.ms-hero__eyebrow Case Study
      h1.ms-hero__heading 300% Revenue Growth in 12 Months
      p.ms-hero__description
        | How we helped a leading fintech startup scale from 10K to 1M users with cloud
        | infrastructure and AI-powered fraud detection.

  //- Case Study Content
  section.ms-pb-24
    .ms-container
      .case-study-layout
        //- Main Content
        div
          //- Challenge
          section.ms-mb-16
            h2.ms-heading-2.ms-mb-6 The Challenge
            p.ms-text-base.ms-leading-relaxed.ms-mb-4
              | PayFlow, a rapidly growing fintech startup, was experiencing severe growing pains.
              | Their legacy infrastructure couldn't handle the surge in transaction volume, and
              | their manual fraud review process was creating a bottleneck that cost them both
              | money and customer trust.
            p.ms-text-base.ms-leading-relaxed.ms-mb-4
              | With a 200% increase in user sign-ups over six months, their existing systems were
              | cracking under pressure. Page load times exceeded 5 seconds during peak hours, and
              | their fraud detection flagged too many legitimate transactions, leading to a 15%
              | false positive rate.
            ul.ms-list-disc.ms-list-inside.ms-space-y-2.ms-mb-6.ms-ml-4
              li Infrastructure couldn't scale beyond 10K concurrent users
              li Manual fraud review delayed transactions by up to 48 hours
              li 15% false positive rate on fraud detection
              li Customer churn rate increasing 3% month-over-month

          //- Solution
          section.ms-mb-16
            h2.ms-heading-2.ms-mb-6 Our Solution
            p.ms-text-base.ms-leading-relaxed.ms-mb-4
              | We implemented a three-phase transformation plan that addressed PayFlow's
              | infrastructure, analytics, and security needs simultaneously.
            h3.ms-heading-4.ms-mb-4.ms-mt-8 Phase 1: Cloud Migration
            p.ms-text-base.ms-leading-relaxed.ms-mb-4
              | We migrated PayFlow's entire infrastructure to a multi-region AWS setup with
              | auto-scaling groups, reducing their infrastructure costs by 40% while increasing
              | capacity by 10x.
            h3.ms-heading-4.ms-mb-4.ms-mt-8 Phase 2: AI-Powered Fraud Detection
            p.ms-text-base.ms-leading-relaxed.ms-mb-4
              | Our machine learning team built a custom fraud detection model trained on
              | PayFlow's transaction data, reducing false positives from 15% to under 2% while
              | catching 99.7% of actual fraudulent transactions.
            h3.ms-heading-4.ms-mb-4.ms-mt-8 Phase 3: Real-Time Analytics
            p.ms-text-base.ms-leading-relaxed.ms-mb-4
              | We deployed a real-time analytics dashboard that gives PayFlow's team instant
              | visibility into transaction patterns, user behavior, and system health.

          //- Results
          section.ms-mb-16
            h2.ms-heading-2.ms-mb-8 The Results
            .metrics-grid
              .metric-card
                .metric-value 300%
                .metric-label Revenue Growth
              .metric-card
                .metric-value 1M+
                .metric-label Active Users
              .metric-card
                .metric-value 99.7%
                .metric-label Fraud Detection Rate

          //- Client Testimonial
          section.ms-mb-16
            .ms-testimonial.ms-testimonial--featured
              blockquote.ms-testimonial__quote
                | "TechCorp didn't just fix our infrastructure â€” they transformed our entire
                | business. The AI fraud detection alone saved us over $2M in the first year, and
                | our customers love the instant transaction processing."
              .ms-testimonial__author
                img.ms-testimonial__avatar(
                  src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472099645785-5658abf4ff4e?w=96&h=96&fit=crop&q=80"
                  alt="Alex Rivera"
                )
                .ms-testimonial__info
                  span.ms-testimonial__name Alex Rivera
                  span.ms-testimonial__title CTO
                  span.ms-testimonial__company PayFlow

          //- CTA Section
          section.ms-py-24
            .ms-container
              a.ms-image-link.ms-image-link--xl.ms-image-link--center.ms-image-link--glow(href="demo.html")
                .ms-image-link__background
                  img.ms-image-link__image(
                    loading="lazy"
                    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556761175-b413da4baf72?w=1920&h=800&fit=crop&q=80"
                    alt="Get similar results"
                  )
                .ms-image-link__overlay
                .ms-image-link__content
                  h2.ms-image-link__title Get Similar Results
                  p.ms-image-link__description
                    | Ready to transform your business? Let's discuss how we can help you achieve
                    | your goals.
                  span.ms-image-link__cta Book a Demo

        //- Sidebar
        aside.case-study-sidebar
          .sidebar-card
            h3(style="font-size: var(--ms-text-lg); font-weight: var(--ms-font-semibold); color: var(--ms-text-primary); margin: 0 0 var(--ms-space-6) 0;") Client Information
            .sidebar-item
              .sidebar-label Client
              .sidebar-value PayFlow
            .sidebar-item
              .sidebar-label Industry
              .sidebar-value FinTech / Financial Services
            .sidebar-item
              .sidebar-label Company Size
              .sidebar-value 50-200 employees
            .sidebar-item
              .sidebar-label Services Used
              .sidebar-value Cloud Infrastructure, AI & ML, Data Analytics
            .sidebar-item
              .sidebar-label Timeline
              .sidebar-value 12 months
            .sidebar-item
              .sidebar-label Region
              .sidebar-value Asia-Pacific
